## 🖥️ Output Compatibility

| Software | Format | Status |
|---|---|---|
| Blender 3.x / 4.x | `.obj` | ✅ Imports with correct geometry, normals, UV |
| Unity 2022 LTS | `.obj` | ✅ Asset import with default settings |
| Unreal Engine 5 | `.obj` | ✅ Import via Content Browser |
| MeshLab | `.obj` | ✅ Renders correctly |
| Windows 3D Viewer | `.obj` | ✅ Opens directly |
| Photoshop / Substance | `.png` normal map | ✅ Blue-channel normal map standard |
| Three.js | `.obj` via OBJLoader | ✅ Correct vertex and UV data |

