## 🧩 Dependencies

| Package | Purpose | Install |
|---|---|---|
| `numpy` | Array math, gradient ops | included above |
| `opencv-python` | Image I/O, Sobel filter, resize | included above |
| `scipy` | Extension fallback (Gaussian) | included above |
| `matplotlib` | 3D interactive preview | included above |
| `trimesh` | Mesh assembly + `.obj` export | included above |
| `pillow` | Save normal map PNG | included above |

